A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoreweave-ipo-stock-price-crwv-ai-nvidia-tech-stocks-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIPO%20at%20%2440%20per%20share%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20stock%20flailed%2C%20opening%20at%20%2439%20per%20share%2C%20then%20falling%20as%20much%20as%206%25%20and%20ending%20the%20day%20back%20up%20at%20%2441.59.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cloud%20firm%2C%20founded%20in%202017%2C%20is%20the%20first%20pure-play%20AI%20public%20offering%20in%20the%20US.%20CoreWeave%20buys%20graphics%20processing%20units%20from%20Nvidia%20and%20then%20pairs%20them%20with%20software%20to%20give%20companies%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20access%20the%20GPUs%20and%20achieve%20the%20top%20performance%20of%20their%20AI%20products%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20financial%20future%20is%20dependent%20on%20two%20unknowns%20%E2%80%94%20that%20the%20use%20and%20usefulness%20of%20AI%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepseek-compute-jevons-paradox-demand-market-ai-stocks-nvidia-chatgpt-2025-1%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSeveral%2520tech%2520leaders%252C%2520such%2520as%2Cwill%2520go%2520up%2520%25E2%2580%2594%2520not%2520down.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrow%20immensely%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20that%20those%20workloads%20will%20continue%20to%20run%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-may-lose-ai-inference-market-groq-cerebras-2024-8%23%3A~%3Atext%3DInference%2520made%2520up%252040%2525%2520of%2Cchips%2520to%2520compete%2520with%2520Nvidia.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%20GPUs.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20no%20wonder%20that%20the%20listing%20has%20often%20been%20described%20as%20a%20bellwether%20for%20the%20entire%20AI%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20CoreWeave's%20specific%20business%20has%20some%20contours%20that%20could%20be%20responsible%20for%20Friday's%20ambivalent%20debut%20without%20passing%20judgment%20on%20AI%20as%20a%20whole.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoreWeave%20customers%20are%20highly%20concentrated%20and%20its%20suppliers%20are%20even%20more%20so.%20The%20company%20is%20highly%20leveraged%2C%20with%20billions%20in%20debt%2C%20collateralized%20by%20GPUs.%20The%20future%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoreweave-ipo-nvidia-gpu-hopper-problem-blackwell-ai-depreciation-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eobsolescence%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20those%20GPUs%20is%20looming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUmesh%20Padval%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20Thomvest%20expects%20the%20pricing%20for%20the%20GPU%20computing%20CoreWeave%20offers%20to%20go%20down%20in%20the%20next%2012%20to%2018%20months%20as%20GPU%20supply%20continues%20to%20improve%2C%20which%20could%20challenge%20the%20company's%20future%20profitability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20general%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20bellwether%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%26quot%3B%20Padval%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298f1cd54-4d94-43c1-8a59-00606ea8fb39%5C%22%3EBeyond%20opening%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20does%20it%20mean%20that%20CoreWeave's%20debut%20didn't%20rise%20to%20meet%20hopes%20and%20expectations%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKarl%20Mozurkewich%2C%20principal%20architect%20at%20cloud%20firm%20Valdi%20told%20BI%20the%20Friday%20IPO%20is%20more%20of%20a%20test%20for%20the%20neocloud%20concept%20than%20for%20AI.%20Neoclouds%20are%20a%20term%20used%20to%20describe%20young%20public%20cloud%20providers%20that%20solely%20focus%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gpus-cpus-parallel-computing-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccelerated%20computing.%3C%2Fa%3E%20They%20often%20use%20Nvidia's%20preferred%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-partner-ddn-strategic-leap-nvidia-ai-infrastructure-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereference%20architecture%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20demonstrate%20the%20best%20possible%20performance%20for%20Nvidia's%20hardware.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20gave%20the%20buch%20a%20shoutout%20at%20the%20company's%20tentpole%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gtc-2025-ceo-jensen-huang-ai-landscape-san-jose-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGTC%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20they%20do%20is%20just%20one%20thing.%20They%20host%20GPUs%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said%20to%20an%20audience%20of%20nearly%2018%2C000.%20%26quot%3BThey%20call%20themselves%20GPU%20clouds%2C%20and%20one%20of%20our%20great%20partners%2C%20CoreWeave%2C%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20going%20public%20and%20we're%20super%20proud%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoreWeave's%20public%20market%20performance%20will%20signal%20what%20shape%20the%20future%20could%20take%20for%20these%20companies%2C%20according%20to%20Mozurkewich.%20Will%20more%20companies%20try%20to%20replicate%20the%20GPU-cloud%20model%3F%20Will%20Nvidia%20seed%20more%20similar%20businesses%3F%20Will%20it%20continue%20to%20give%20neoclouds%20early%20access%20to%20new%20hardware%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20industry%20is%20very%20interested%20to%20see%20if%20the%20shape%20of%20CoreWeave%20is%20long-term%20successful%2C%26quot%3B%20Mozurkewich%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDaniel%20Newman%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20Futurum%20Group%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20CoreWeave%20is%20%26quot%3Bone%20measuring%20point%20of%20the%20AI%20trade%3B%20it%20isn't%20entirely%20indicative%20of%20the%20overall%20AI%20market%20or%20AI%20demand.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20the%20company%20has%20the%20opportunity%20to%20improve%20its%20fate%20as%20AI%20scales%20and%20the%20customer%20base%20grows%20and%20diversifies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELucas%20Keh%2C%20Semiconductors%20Analyst%20at%20Third%20Bridge%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCurrently%2C%20more%20than%2070%25%20of%20CoreWeave's%20revenue%20comes%20from%20hyperscalers%2C%20but%20our%20experts%20expect%20this%20concentration%20to%20decrease%201%E2%80%942%20years%20after%20an%20IPO%20as%20the%20company%20diversifies%20its%20customer%20base%20beyond%20public%20cloud%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20Keh%20said%20via%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20handful%20of%20large%2C%20dominant%20enterprise%20customers%20is%20not%20uncommon%20for%20a%20young%20provider%20like%20CoreWeave%2C%20Mozurkewich%20said.%20But%20it's%20also%20no%20surprise%20that%20it%20could%20concern%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20where%20CoreWeave%20has%20a%20chance%20to%20shine%20as%20AI%20and%20the%20demand%20for%20AI%20spans%20beyond%20the%20big%207%20to%2010%20names.%20The%20caveat%20will%20be%20how%20stable%20GPU%20prices%20are%20as%20availability%20increases%20and%20competition%20increases%2C%26quot%3B%20Newman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20issues%2C%20like%20obsolescence%2C%20the%20necessary%20depreciation%2C%20and%20leverage%20will%20be%20harder%20to%20shake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%20or%20an%20insight%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20Emma%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aecosgrove%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eecosgrove%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20use%20the%20secure%20messaging%20app%20Signal%3A%20443-333-9088%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoreweave-weak-ipo-ai-skepticism-nvidia-gpu-neocloud-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743199063000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67e704b069253ccddf9aaa87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoreweave-weak-ipo-ai-skepticism-nvidia-gpu-neocloud-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CoreWeave's%20IPO%20debut%20tests%20neocloud%20viability%20and%20reliance%20on%20Nvidia%20GPUs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ecosgrove%40businessinsider.com%20(Emma%20Cosgrove)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%