0John%20Waldron%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0to%20use%20its%20jets%20for%20personal%20travel%20and%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20primary%20use%20of%20our%20corporate%20aircraft%20is%20to%20facilitate%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BOur%20CEO%20and%20COO%20are%20expected%20to%20use%20our%20corporate%20aircraft%2C%20including%20for%20personal%20travel%2C%20for%20security%20reasons%2C%20as%20well%20as%20to%20maximize%20the%20efficiency%20of%20their%20travel%20time%20and%20their%20availability%20for%20firm%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20associate%20will%20be%20part%20of%20the%20corporate%20aviation%20integrated%20services%20team%20within%20the%20executive%20office%2C%20a%20division%20that%20encompasses%20units%20like%20marketing%2C%20corporate%20communications%2C%20and%20some%20philanthropic%20and%20public-facing%20programs.%20It's%20helmed%20by%20Russell%20Horwitz%2C%20the%20bank's%20chief%20of%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%E2%80%A6%20does%20the%20gig%20sound%20like%20one%20for%20you%3F%20Before%20you%20buckle%20up%20your%20seatbelt%20and%20tap%20the%20intercom%20for%20a%20glass%20of%20Champagne%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20know%20that%20this%20role%20appears%20to%20be%20based%20on%20the%20ground%20%E2%80%94%20not%20in%20a%20plush%20leather%20recliner%20in%20the%20air%2C%20enjoying%20a%20view%20over%20the%20wings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20job%20post%2C%20this%20associate%20will%20be%20focused%20on%20tasks%20such%20as%20assuming%20%26quot%3Boperations%20%26amp%3B%20financial%20oversight%20of%20the%20firm's%20executive%20aviation%20program%2C%20including%20business%20owned%20aircraft%20%26amp%3B%20fractional%20aircraft%20interest.%26quot%3B%20The%20person%20will%20assemble%20reports%2C%20perform%20some%20bookkeeping%20activities%2C%20and%20develop%20policies%20and%20procedures%20relating%20to%20the%20aviation%20program.%20They'll%20also%20%26quot%3Bassist%20with%20all%20aviation%20operational%20matte