yright%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%204o%20image%20generation%20tool%2C%20made%20available%20for%20paying%20ChatGPT%20users%20this%20week%2C%20allows%20people%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghibli-ai-trend-viral-response-heartwarming-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etransform%20images%20into%20the%20style%20of%20Studio%20Ghibli%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Japanese%20studio%20behind%20anime%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BSpirited%20Away%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BThe%20Boy%20and%20the%20Heron.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20anime%20studio%20brings%20a%20copyright%20lawsuit%20to%20stop%20Open%20AI%20from%20offering%20the%20feature%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20been%20used%20to%20make%20Studio%20Ghibli-style%20images%20of%20everything%20from%20people's%20cats%20to%20the%209%2F11%20attack%20on%20the%20Twin%20Towers%20%E2%80%94%20it%20would%20have%20a%20hard%20time%20winning%20in%20court%2C%20copyright%20lawyers%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rules%20around%20using%20Studio%20Ghibli's%20movies%20to%20train%20OpenAI's%20models%20are%20not%20yet%20legally%20settled%2C%20and%20copyright%20laws%20generally%20allow%20artists%20to%20mimic%20a%20visual%20style%2C%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ghibli-style%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecapability%2C%20promoted%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-good-tweet-twink-image-generator-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20a%20step%20forward%20from%20ChatGPT's%20previous%20image%20generation%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20versions%20of%20ChatGPT%2C%20like%20the%20one%20using%20the%20DALL-E%203%20engine%2C%20which%20is%20still%20available%20in%20the%20free%20version%2C%20make%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-studio-ghibli-style-images-violate-copyright-or-not-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifficult%20to%20create%20images%20in%20the%20style%20of%20living%20artists%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20safeguard%20is%20less%20about%20copyright%20protection%20than%20about%20public%20optics%2C%20Matthew%20Sag%2C%20an%20Emory%20University%20law%20professor%20studying%20copyright%20law%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOpenAI%20took%20a%20pretty%20sensible%20decision%20to%20say%2C%20'We%20are%20going%20to%20stop%20producing%20images%20in%20the%20style%20of%20living%20people%2C'%26quot%3B%20Sag%20said.%20%26quot%3BNot%20because%20it's%20copyright%20infringement%2C%20but%20because%20people%20don't%20like%20that.%20Individuals%20get%20very%20understandably%20viscerally%20upset%20by%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20X%2C%20OpenAI%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20reacted%20to%20the%20viral%20Ghiblification%20by%20saying%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bput%20a%20lot%20of%20thought%20into%20the%20initial%20examples%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20new%20technology.%20He%20wrote%20the%20new%20image-generation%20features%20had%20become%20so%20popular%20that%20%26quot%3Bour%20GPUs%20are%20melting%26quot%3B%20and%20he'd%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-chatgpt-studio-ghibli-style-images-generation-grok-claude-genai-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimpose%20rate%20limits%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20trying%20to%20make%20it%20more%20efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c5fae2ca-c9de-4a61-b454-72041d1395bf%5C%22%3EStudio%20Ghibli%20could%20bring%20two%20kinds%20of%20copyright%20cases%20against%20OpenAI%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20copyright%20disputes%20surrounding%20ChatGPT%20and%20generative%20artificial%20intelligence%20remain%20hotly%20disputed%20in%20the%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreators%20have%20brought%20dozens%20of%20lawsuits%20across%20the%20country%20against%20OpenAI%20and%20other%20generative%20AI%20companies.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20federal%20judge%20in%20Manhattan%20allowed%20the%20bulk%20of%20one%20of%20the%20