illed%20with%20Ghiblified%20photos%20of%20the%209%2F11%20terror%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20hanging%20out%20with%20Donald%20Trump%20at%20Mar-a-Lago%2C%20or%20the%20JFK%20assassination%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20have%20gone%20viral%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20even%20got%20in%20on%20the%20action%2C%20posting%20a%20Ghibli-style%20image%20of%20ICE%20arresting%20a%20sobbing%20woman%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20selling%20fentanyl%20while%20living%20in%20the%20US%20illegally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22zxx%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPVdINmsHXs%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPVdINmsHXs%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FBw5YUCI2xL%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FBw5YUCI2xL%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20The%20White%20House%20(%40WhiteHouse)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWhiteHouse%2Fstatus%2F1905332049021415862%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2027%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20OpenAI%20spokesperson%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20its%20policies%20allow%20the%20generation%20of%20images%20in%20%26quot%3Bbroader%20studio%20styles%26quot%3B%20but%20not%20%26quot%3Bthe%20style%20of%20a%20living%20artist.%26quot%3B%20But%20Kristelia%20Garc%C3%ADa%2C%20an%20intellectual%20property%20law%20professor%20at%20Georgetown%20University%20Law%2C%20said%20the%20distinction%20between%20copying%20the%20work%20of%20Studio%20Ghibli%20or%20cofounder%20Hayao%20Miyazaki%20was%20irrelevant.%20The%20studio%2C%20and%20possibly%20individual%20artists%20working%20for%20it%2C%20could%20bring%20a%20copyright%20claim%2C%20Garc%C3%ADa%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20s