tated%20that%20in%202013%20she%20came%20to%20know%20that%20the%20Army%20officer%20was%20already%20married.%20When%20she%20confronted%20Singh%20over%20his%20marital%20status%2C%20he%20told%20her%20he%20was%20about%20to%20divorce%20his%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20he%20started%20delaying%20marriage%20with%20the%20survivor%20on%20some%20pretext%20or%20the%20other%20and%20cooked%20up%20stories%20like%20his%20parents%20were%20unwell%2C%20according%20to%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2024%2C%202025%2C%20the%20survivor%20came%20to%20know%20that%20the%20Army%20officer%20was%20in%20simultaneous%20relationships%20with%20other%20women%20whom%20also%20he%20had%20promised%20to%20marry%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20police%20constable%20contacted%20Singh%2C%20currently%20posted%20with%20the%20Army%20Service%20Corps%20(Mechanized%20Transport)%20battalion%20and%20questioned%20him%20about%20his%20relationships%2C%20he%20started%20arguing%20and%20said%20he%20won't%20marry%20her%20now%2C%20said%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVarun%20told%20me%20that%20if%20I%20lodge%20a%20complaint%2C%20he%20will%20bump%20me%20off%20and%20hang%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20survivor%20stated%20in%20her%20complaint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743185160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Ftg1hlnoo_madhya-pradesh-police_625x300_07_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-officer-charged-with-raping-madhya-pradesh-cop-on-pretext-of-marriage-8035257%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Army%20officer%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20allegedly%20raping%20a%20female%20constable%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20police%20posted%20in%20Bhopal%20city%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20marriage%20in%20an%20