e%20struck%20the%20region.%20On%20the%20streets%20and%20shopping%20malls%2C%20people%20screamed%20in%20panic%20before%20they%20were%20evacuated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFraser%20Morton%2C%20a%20tourist%20who%20was%20in%20one%20of%20Bangkok's%20many%20malls%20shopping%20for%20camera%20equipment%2C%20said%20when%20the%20building%20began%20to%20move%20there%20was%20panic%20and%20people%20were%20%26quot%3Brunning%20the%20wrong%20way%20down%20the%20escalators%2C%26quot%3B%20news%20agency%20AP%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20this%20building%20right%20behind%20me.%20It%20was%20a%20shopping%20mall%20and%20I%20was%20there%20to%20buy%20camera%20equipment.%20And%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20the%20whole%20building%20just%20began%20to%20move.%20Immediately%20there%20was%20screaming%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20panic%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Morton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20started%20walking%20calmly%20at%20first%2C%20but%20then%20the%20building%20started%20really%20moving.%20And%20yeah%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20screaming%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20panic.%20People%20running%20the%20wrong%20way%20down%20the%20escalators%2C%20like%20lots%20of%20banging%20and%20crashing%20inside%20the%20mall.%20I%20got%20outside%20and%20then%20looked%20up%20at%20the%20building%2C%20that%20one%20there%2C%20and%20this%20whole%20building%20was%20just%20moving.%20Dust%20and%20debris%20-%20it%20was%20pretty%20intense%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaul%20Vincent%2C%20a%20tourist%20from%20England%2C%20saw%20water%20coming%20from%20the%20top%20of%20one%20tall%20building%20and%20other%20buildings%20swaying.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20screaming%20and%20panicking%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20sitting%20in%20a%20bar%20and%20restaurant...%20just%20talking%20to%20a%20stranger%20there%2C%20and%20the%20next%20thing%2C%20because%20it%20was%20a%20small%20bar%2C%20we%20just%20felt%20a%20movement...%20But%20the%20next%20thing%2C%20everybody%20came%20on%20the%20street.%20So%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20screaming%20and%20panicking%2C%20which%20obviously%20made%20it%20a%20lot%20worse%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Vincent%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20earthquake%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20strong%206.4%20magnitude%20aftershock%2C%20and%20people%20in%20Bangkok%20evacuated%20from%20their%20buildings%20were%20cautioned%20to%20stay%20outside%20in%20case%20there%20were%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20high-rise%20building%20under%20construction%20in%20Bangkok%20collapsed.%20The%20police%20told%20AP%20they%20were%20responding%20to%20the%20scene%20near%20Bangkok's%20popular%20Chatuchak%20Market%2C%20and%20had%20no%20immediate%20information%20on%20how%20many%20workers%20were%20on%20the%20site%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20magnitude%207.7%20earthquake%20caused%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20to%20evacuate%20from%20their%20homes%20and%20workplaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Geological%20Survey%20and%20Germany's%20GFZ%20centre%20for%20geosciences%20said%20the%20earthquake%20was%20a%20shallow%2010%20km%2C%20with%20an%20epicentre%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20according%20to%20preliminary%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20greater%20Bangkok%20area%20is%20home%20to%20more%20than%2017%20million%20people%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20live%20in%20high-rise%20apartments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quakes%20wrought%20widespread%20damage%2C%20particularly%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20where%20buildings%20fell%20onto%20their%20sides%2C%20roads%20cracked%20open%2C%20and%20the%20well-known%20Ava%20bridge%20collapsed%20near%20the%20epicentre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20capital%20Naypyidaw%2C%20news%20agency%20AFP%20reported%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20emergency%20department%20at%20the%20city's%20main%20hospital%20pancaked%20onto%20a%20car.%20Wounded%20at%20the%201%2C000-bed%20facility%20were%20being%20treated%20outside%2C%20intravenous%20drips%20hanging%20from%20their%20gurneys.%20Some%