3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family's%20lawyer%20suspects%20that%20Mr%20Suman's%20personal%20documents%20were%20misused.%20%26quot%3BSomeone%20has%20used%20Prince's%20documents%20by%20fraud.%20We%20have%20approached%20both%20the%20police%20and%20tax%20authorities%20to%20probe%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20March%2020%20notice%2C%20the%20I-T%20department%20sought%20a%20detailed%20breakdown%20of%20financial%20transactions%20totaling%20%E2%82%B949.24%20crore.%20They%20also%20sought%20documents%20like%20bills%2C%20purchase%20vouchers%2C%20transportation%20records%20and%20bank%20statements%20for%20the%20financial%20year%202022-23.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Suman%20is%20not%20alone.%20Md%20Rahees%2C%20a%20juice%20vendor%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Aligarh%2C%20has%20received%20an%20I-T%20notice%20of%20over%20Rs%207.5%20crore%2C%20sending%20him%20and%20his%20family%20into%20a%20tizzy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20why%20this%20notice%20has%20been%20issued.%20I%20only%20sell%20juice.%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20so%20much%20money.%20What%20should%20I%20do%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rahees%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20request%20the%20government%20to%20help%20me.%20I%20am%20a%20poor%20man.%20I%20should%20not%20be%20implicated%20in%20a%20false%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notice%20pointed%20at%20%26quot%3Bbogus%26quot%3B%20transactions%20worth%20crores%20in%202020-21%20in%20his%20name.%20Thus%2C%20he%20owed%20the%20government%20GST%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%207%2C79%2C02%2C457.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20approached%20the%20I-T%20authorities%20who%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20had%20shared%20my%20personal%20documents%20with%20anyone.%20I%20said%20I%20never%20shared%20them%20with%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rahees%2C%20who%20stays%20in%20Tar%20Wali%20Gali%20under%20Banna%20Devi%20police%20station%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahees's%20mother%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20struggle%20for%20our%20daily%20meals...%20If%20we%20had%20so%20much%20money%2C%20why%20would%20our%20son%20have%20to%20work%20so%20hard%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20a%20preliminary%20probe%20revealed%20that%20Rahees's%20personal%20documents%20were%20fraudulently%20used%20for%20donating%20crores%20of%20rupees%20for%20the%202022%20Punjab%20assembly%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Rahees%20was%20a%20millionaire%2C%20would%20he%20run%20a%20juice%20shop%3F%20This%20is%20definitely%20a%20case%20of%20fraud%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20juice%20seller's%20friend%2C%20Sohail%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20Adnan%20Khan%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743176220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F5nu1181o_up-gst-copy_625x300_28_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fegg-seller-juice-vendor-get-notices-for-gst-dues-worth-crores-uttar-pradesh-aligarh-madhya-pradesh-damoh-8034273%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20egg%20seller%20and%20a%20juice%20vendor%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20were%20in%20for%20a%20huge%20shock%20when%20they%20received%20notices%20for%20dues%20worth%20crores%20from%20the%20Income%20Tax%20(I-T)%20department.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fegg-seller-juice-vendor-get-notices-for-gst-dues-worth-crores-uttar-pradesh-aligarh-madhya-pradesh-damoh-8034273%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anjini%20on%20working%20with%20Salman%3B%20advice%20given%20by%20Varun%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743176101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119663452%2Cimgsize-43098.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbol