iland%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20powerful%20earthquake%20of%20magnitude%207.7%20centred%20in%20the%20Sagaing%20region%20near%20the%20Myanmar%20city%20of%20Mandalay%20caused%20extensive%20damage%20in%20that%20country%20and%20also%20shook%20neighbouring%20Thailand%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHOW%20VULNERABLE%20IS%20MYANMAR%20TO%20EARTHQUAKES%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMyanmar%20lies%20on%20the%20boundary%20between%20two%20tectonic%20plates%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20seismically%20active%20countries%2C%20although%20large%20and%20destructive%20earthquakes%20have%20been%20relatively%20rare%20in%20the%20Sagaing%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20plate%20boundary%20between%20the%20India%20Plate%20and%20Eurasia%20Plate%20runs%20approximately%20north-south%2C%20cutting%20through%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Joanna%20Faure%20Walker%2C%20a%20professor%20and%20earthquake%20expert%20at%20University%20College%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20plates%20move%20past%20each%20other%20horizontally%20at%20different%20speeds.%20While%20this%20causes%20%26quot%3Bstrike%20slip%26quot%3B%20quakes%20that%20are%20normally%20less%20powerful%20than%20those%20seen%20in%20%26quot%3Bsubduction%20zones%26quot%3B%20like%20Sumatra%2C%20where%20one%20plate%20slides%20under%20another%2C%20they%20can%20still%20reach%20magnitudes%20of%207%20to%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHY%20WAS%20FRIDAY'S%20QUAKE%20SO%20DAMAGING%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESagaing%20has%20been%20hit%20by%20several%20quakes%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20with%20a%206.8%20magnitude%20event%20causing%20at%20least%2026%20deaths%20and%20dozens%20of%20injuries%20in%20late%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Friday's%20event%20was%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20the%20biggest%26quot%3B%20to%20hit%20Myanmar's%20mainland%20in%20three%20quarters%20of%20a%20century%2C%20said%20Bill%20McGuire%2C%20another%20earthquake%20expert%20at%20UCL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoger%20Musson%2C%20honorary%20research%20fellow%20at%20the%20British%20Geological%20Survey%2C%20told%20Reuters%20that%20the%20shallow%20depth%20of%20the%20quake%20meant%20the%20damage%20would%20be%20more%20severe.%20The%20quake's%20epicentre%20was%20at%20a%20depth%20of%20just%2010%20km%20(6.2%20miles)%2C%20according%20to%20the%20United%20States%20Geological%20Survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20very%20damaging%20because%20it%20has%20occurred%20at%20a%20shallow%20depth%2C%20so%20the%20shockwaves%20are%20not%20dissipated%20as%20they%20go%20from%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20earthquake%20up%20to%20the%20surface.%20The%20buildings%20received%20the%20full%20force%20of%20the%20shaking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20not%20to%20be%20focused%20on%20epicentres%20because%20the%20seismic%20waves%20don't%20radiate%20out%20from%20the%20epicentre%20-%20they%20radiate%20out%20from%20the%20whole%20line%20of%20the%20fault%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHOW%20PREPARED%20WAS%20MYANMAR%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20USGS%20Earthquake%20Hazards%20Program%20said%20on%20Friday%20that%20fatalities%20could%20be%20between%2010%2C000%20and%20100%2C000%20people%2C%20and%20the%20economic%20impact%20could%20be%20as%20high%20as%2070%25%20of%20Myanmar's%20GDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusson%20said%20such%20forecasts%20are%20based%20on%20data%20from%20past%20earthquakes%20and%20on%20Myanmar's%20size%2C%20location%20and%20overall%20quake%20readiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relative%20rarity%20of%20large%20seismic%20events%20in%20the%20Sagaing%20region%20-%20which%20is%20close%20to%20heavily%20populated%20Mandalay%20-%20means%20that%20infrastructure%20had%20not%20been%20built%20to%20withstand%20them.%20That%20means%20the%20damage%20could%20end%20up%20being%20far%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusson%20said%20that%20the%20last%20major%20quake%20to%20hit%20the%20region%20was%20in%201956%2C%20and%20homes%20are%20unlikely%20to%20have%20been%20built%20to%20withstand%20seismic%20forces%20as%20powerful%20as%20those%20that%20hit%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20the%20seismicity%20in%20Myanmar%20is%20further%20to%20the%20west%20whereas%20this%20is%20running%20down%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743174600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fe8v58vn8_myanmar-quake_625x300_28_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthailand-earthquake-updates-explained-what-caused-the-powerful-earthquake-in-myanmar-thailand-8034108%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20powerful%20earthquake%20of%20magnitude%207.7%20centred%20in%20the%20Sagaing%20region%20near%20the%20Myanmar%20city%20of%20Mandalay%20caused%20extensive%20damage%20in%20that%20country%20and%20also%20shook%20neighbouring%20Thailand%20on%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthailand-earthquake-updates-explained-what-caused-the-powerful-earthquake-in-myanmar-thailand-8034108%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dhoni%20Magic%20Lights%20Up%20IPL%202025%20Once%20Again%2C%20Stuns%20Everyone%20With%20Quick%20Stumping%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E%20produced%20a%20lighting%20quick%20stumping%20once%20again%20to%20leave%20everyone%20stunned%20during%20the%20IPL%202025%20encounter%20between%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20and%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20on%20Friday.%20It%20was%20a%20trademark%20effort%20from