sting%20opinions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20arrested%20on%20June%2018%2C%201946.%20But%20there%20followed%20a%20rallying%20cry%20for%20her%20release.%20Over%20forty%20women%20marched%20to%20the%20station.%20They%20demanded%20that%20she%20be%20released.%20The%20alternative%20they%20proposed%20was%20that%20they%20be%20arrested.%20When%20Vatsala%20was%20questioned%20about%20her%20speech%20by%20the%20officers%2C%20she%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CJust%20as%20the%20words%20%E2%80%98Viva%20Salazar%E2%80%99%20fill%20you%20with%20pride%2C%20so%20does%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Hind%E2%80%99%20galvanise%20my%20spirit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20impossible%20to%20speak%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F394377%2Fmg-motor-india-launch-unchartered-roads-campaign-to-celebrate-works-of-women-human-trafficking-everest-tribal-welfare%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erebellious%20spirits%20of%20the%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Goa%20without%20mentioning%20Berta%20de%20Menezes%20Braganca.%20Whether%20it%20was%20partaking%20in%20protest%20marches%20and%20speeches%20in%20South%20Goa%2C%20starting%20a%20fortnightly%20%E2%80%98Free%20Goa%E2%80%99%20in%20Mumbai%20in%201958%2C%20or%20even%20demanding%20military%20action%20against%20the%20colonisers%20through%20speeches%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20India%2C%20Berta%20did%20not%20back%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20also%20chief%20of%20the%20Goa%20wing%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress.%20A%20story%20that%20is%20often%20retold%20is%20of%20how%20she%20and%20her%20uncle%20TB%20Cunha%20were%20prevented%20from%20speaking%20at%20a%20certain%20event%20on%20June%2030%2C%201946%2C%20in%2