p%3EThe%20156%20choppers%20would%20be%20divided%20between%20the%20Indian%20Army%20(90)%20and%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20for%20operations%20along%20the%20China%20and%20Pakistan%20borders%20and%20would%20be%20a%20major%20step%20towards%20creating%20jobs%20and%20expanding%20the%20aerospace%20ecosystem%20within%20the%20country%2C%20defence%20sources%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHAL%20received%20the%20tender%20for%20156%20LCH%20in%20June%20last%20year.%20The%20IAF%20is%20the%20lead%20agency%20for%20this%20joint%20procurement%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20LCH%2C%20which%20is%20also%20known%20as%20the%20Prachand%2C%20is%20the%20world's%20only%20attack%20helicopter%20that%20can%20land%20and%20take%20off%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%205%2C000%20meters%20(16%2C400%20feet)%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20ideal%20to%20operate%20in%20the%20high-altitude%20areas%20of%20the%20Siachen%20glacier%20and%20eastern%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prachand%20is%20capable%20of%20firing%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20air-to-ground%20and%20air-to-air%20missiles%20and%20can%20destroy%20enemy's%20air%20defence%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20been%20emphasising%20the%20intention%20to%20go%20for%20self-reliance%20in%20defence%20manufacturing%20through%20Make%20in%20India%20as%20part%20of%20Atmanirbhar%20Bharat%20initiatives.%20The%20government%20has%20placed%20the%20biggest%20order%20for%20indigenous%20defence%20systems%20including%2083%20Light%20Combat%20Aircraft%20(LCA)%20and%20is%20in%20the%20process%20of%20ordering%2097%20more%20for%20which%20the%20negotiations%20have%20been%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Cabinet%20Committee%20on%20Security%20recently%20cleared%20the%20deal%20for%20307%20ATAGS%20howitzers%20and%20the%20deal%20for%20it%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20signed%20on%20Wednesday.%20The%20Rs%207%2C000%20crore%20deal%20is%20divided%20between%20two%20companies%2C%20including%20Bharat%20Forge%20and%20the%20Tata%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5